description: This is a tool/ skill that will help the user find the minecraft block id quick and effecient. This process would normally take about twenty minutes to find a reliable site for the ids. But with this skill it will allow Alexa to go and retrieve it for you in a much shorter time.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, open command block and what is the id for stone
Alexa tell command block to what is minecraft id for polished andesite
name: commandBlock
shortDescription: This skill is a quick efficient way to retrieve minecraft block ids to help speed up the process to find the block id in minecraft.
